data.title: Naima B. Robert – SISTERS Magazine
data.meta_description: Audio Lecture • Naima B. Robert - SISTERS Magazine • Muslim Central
data.text:
Sisters, are you waiting for inspiration to turn your life

around? Sometimes all it takes is a single seed.

Sisters is a monthly magazine for sisters, by sisters, inspiration

for Muslim women everywhere to fulfill their potential looking

for spiritual, emotional and intellectual growth. Look no

further. Sisters magazine is here
